{"tid":1257415,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 關心TVB新聞部經理袁志偉與\"小精靈\"們的方法","createTime":"2019-06-25T14:09:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T22:47:37.000Z","uid":217418,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0675816a247a19e97b28c6408fb7bacfffe26d45","tid":1257415,"uid":217418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:09:56.000Z","msg":"袁志偉事蹟:<br />\n<br />\n河蟹「張融」起源短片<br />\n2014年7月中旬，工聯會發起「反暴力反拉布」遊行，一名參與遊行的女士接受無綫新聞訪問時，笑稱支持政府及「反中央」，後獲身邊人「提水」才急急改口稱到場「反佔中」，又指不滿立法會有議員「丟來丟去」，所以支持「『張融』（應為周融之誤）的和平（方案）」。<br />\n傳聞TVB新聞部話事人袁志偉，知道此街訪出街後勃然大怒，下令要「抽走阿姐」，認為這個街訪抹黑北京，結果當天午間新聞和六點半新聞報導都河蟹了此街訪。袁志偉這種河蟹做法，令到很多網民不滿...<br />\n<br />\n2014年10月15日於香港發生的雨傘革命，無綫新聞拍攝到七名警員將一名被捕疑犯，帶到公園涉嫌圍毆，影片長約4分鐘，無綫早上的新聞報道播出該片段，有「抬到暗角、拳打腳踢」等旁白及字幕，後來時段的新聞報道播出的版本，該等旁白及字幕卻遭刪除。同日，袁志偉回應時表示：「報道需要客觀，不能夠主觀判斷。」眾多網民認為上述改動乃袁志偉施壓所致，當晚引來無綫新聞部大部分員工以聲援方式對管理層的作風表達遺憾。事後有疑似無綫新聞部內部會議錄音流出，錄音中，袁志偉質疑，「我哋憑乜野話警員將佢拖至暗角拳打腳踢，你係嗰幾個警察心裡面嗰條蟲？特登拖佢去暗角拳打腳踢？憑乜野呀？」（我們憑甚麼說警察將他帶至暗角拳打腳踢，你知道那幾個警察心裡想甚麼？特意帶他到暗角拳打腳踢？憑甚麼？）[7]事件引致無綫新聞部數十員工聯署，對管理層刪去旁述表示「極度不安」和「無法苟同」<br />\n<br />\n2019年6月12日<br />\n無綫新聞在反送中的報導完全扭曲事相，報導嚴重偏袒警方和政府<br />\n在新聞中完全不播放及不提及：<br />\n1. 警方違法向多名記者開槍，棍打記者<br />\n2. 警方違法瞄準市民頭部發射布袋彈和橡膠子彈<br />\n3. 在沒有任何襲擊下，警方違法向婦孺、伯伯開槍<br />\n等等<br />\n<br />\n2019年6月24日<br />\n在新聞中側重於播放幾位市民的不滿, 而忽略示威者們的眾多訴求<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XnOLC2F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXnOLC2F.jpg&h=b1e48ba9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(袁志偉表示，自2014年10月發生七警涉嫌打人事件後，他的電郵地址及電話都被放上高登討論區，自此就收到許多無訂閱過的電郵，「日日炸我版，百多二百個email來找我」，至今還繼續收到垃圾電郵。)<br />\n<br />\nMORE:<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%A2%81%E5%BF%97%E5%81%89_(%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%25A2%2581%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%2581%2589_%28%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDq6fvQnHzZYMiebojCBKDlo%3D&h=c6128426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%A2%81%E5%BF%97%E5%81%89_(%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85</a>)<br />\n<a href=\"https://evchk.wikia.org/zh/wiki/%E8%A2%81%E5%BF%97%E5%81%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.org%2Fzh%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%25A2%2581%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%2581%2589&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDq6fvQnHzZYMiebojCBKDlo%3D&h=99e0cea3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://evchk.wikia.org/zh/wiki/%E8%A2%81%E5%BF%97%E5%81%89</a><br />\n<br />\n(頭盔: 以下個人資料轉載自維基)<br />\n袁志偉<br />\nKeith Yuen Chi Wai<br />\n電視廣播有限公司助理總經理（新聞及資訊）<br />\n1956年出生<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另外，其實d&ldquo;小精靈&rdquo; 都好需要大家關心</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>到底有咩方法可以煩到d&ldquo;小精靈&rdquo;，但係又唔會煩到d一般市民呢？</strong>（塞地鐵同稅局似乎唔係一個好方法? 根本搞唔到林病，話唔定林病仲係屋企一邊睇電視一邊喺度笑）<br />\n<br />\n［長期頂置］612野餐前捉Pokemon指南<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1203672/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1203672/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n呢度咁多高手，相信一定會諗到個好方法嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc307b18fc4747a3ec0b7395154e4bb4cc544538","tid":1257415,"uid":217418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:13:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf34636cb0085c0ded5347b621fca7133aacd913","tid":1257415,"uid":217418,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:15:18.000Z","msg":"20190623 民陣追究警察濫權集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1254926/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1254926/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n好有用 必看"},{"pid":"12dafe46b719057e8a01bdebe4a5cf0e0f6769d4","tid":1257415,"uid":217418,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:18:38.000Z","msg":"[集合大家力量] 關於TVB報導反送中一事, 我地可以向通訊事務管理局投訴<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1239196/page/3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1239196/page/3</a>"},{"pid":"22da244d0618e8d599e54bee6d602206e805367d","tid":1257415,"uid":217418,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:30:48.000Z","msg":"2014..<br />\n其後網上流出袁志偉因為「拳打腳踢」斥責TVB新聞工作者的錄音，當中袁志偉質疑下屬因並非涉事警員「心入面條蟲」而不應妄下判斷，令該詞成為網絡潮語以及抽水目標，有線新聞在一則報道中更以錄音內容「二次創作」<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">無綫電視總經理李寶安</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />向全體員工發出電郵，表示對偷錄行為十分不認同。李寶安指偷錄是「卑鄙和懦弱」的行為，公司感到震驚，指新聞部內竟「涉嫌存在害群之馬」，令同事的「品格和專業蒙污」，又稱這是「不道德」的做法和「卑鄙手段」，以「斷章取義」方式在網上發放，表示不排除有個別同事「被外間人士利用，意圖破壞公司運作和聲譽」，會嚴正處理。及後，網上隨即出現一段長26分鐘的懷疑足本錄音，似回應李寶安「斷章取義」之說.."},{"pid":"46bf2133ef2679383d1177ea9a6e73f67084acd3","tid":1257415,"uid":217418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:32:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4671cb650a05dd0a0d20e6342c9753c42f47a641","tid":1257415,"uid":217418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:40:15.000Z","msg":"top"},{"pid":"080677f67511038165c34d56166bdd6b56c155c5","tid":1257415,"uid":217418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T17:14:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e87892af16b054c86fe25efca2cfa1cbf973ae0","tid":1257415,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T17:16:55.000Z","msg":"一日唔搞TVs 一日都仆街"},{"pid":"8969769ae5d59cd36464b751c40935996637d5c9","tid":1257415,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e87892af16b054c86fe25efca2cfa1cbf973ae0","tid":1257415,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T17:16:55.000Z","msg":"一日唔搞TVs 一日都仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T17:17:06.000Z","msg":"Tvb"},{"pid":"1b4dbf25b43fdb8441aef8fb8cc8ef4f3ddadae6","tid":1257415,"uid":217418,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5e87892af16b054c86fe25efca2cfa1cbf973ae0","tid":1257415,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T17:16:55.000Z","msg":"一日唔搞TVs 一日都仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T05:17:28.000Z","msg":"對呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"747647bff2158e27a110778a8e5a7a8c50fd636e","tid":1257415,"uid":217418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T05:50:55.000Z","msg":"頭先張建宗喺記者會表示： 唔需要成立獨立調查委員會&hellip;&hellip; 利用現有機制例如監警會就可以<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係大家都知監警會係冇牙老虎，裡面成員全部都係由特首委任<br />\n<br />\nGoogle下 曾健超／鄭仲恆訪問就知道"},{"pid":"ebfa7c328574a55e5399bc405b2118f674764cdf","tid":1257415,"uid":264426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T05:56:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"689463f632aad1f468a5dc2e3f88e3bf79981c52","tid":1257415,"uid":174541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T05:58:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">開咗個tg channel幫大家整合網上可以點樣「發表意見」!<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAFjsHjGSqWCiqNMZXA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAFjsHjGSqWCiqNMZXA&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDq6fvQnHzZYMiebojCBKDlo%3D&h=4c2b98f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAFjsHjGSqWCiqNMZXA</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"ae5b391b1f78682aca4a650da912f5730d304d25","tid":1257415,"uid":217418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"689463f632aad1f468a5dc2e3f88e3bf79981c52","tid":1257415,"uid":174541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T05:58:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">開咗個tg channel幫大家整合網上可以點樣「發表意見」!<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAFjsHjGSqWCiqNMZXA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAFjsHjGSqWCiqNMZXA&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDq6fvQnHzZYMiebojCBKDlo%3D&h=4c2b98f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAFjsHjGSqWCiqNMZXA</a></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T15:14:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />