:"抵制tvb運動，請即讚好<br />\n6月23日下午3:24 &middot; <br />\n睇睇TVB當年係點請人，大家明點解TVB變到咁墮落？<br />\n<br />\n無綫電視新聞部續有人事變動。《am730》報道，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新聞總監袁志偉高薪招聘了民建聯前總幹事陸漢德，入主新聞部擔任編輯主任(Managing Editor)</span></strong>，主力負責本地政治新聞的審稿工作。<br />\n<br />\n陸漢德1979年大學畢業，曾在《文匯報》、《TVBS》及《天天日報》當編採工作。陸漢德自2004年起加入民建聯研究部，2011年晉升至總幹事。民建聯主席譚耀宗指陸漢德去年已退休離開。<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，無綫電視新聞部部分員工得悉陸漢德出任編輯主任後反應極大，有人質疑公司聘請有濃厚政治色彩的建制派人士當重要崗位的動機，擔心未來的新聞報道手法及用語，勢必審查加劇。<br />\n<br />\n誠邀各界加入「監察TVB行動組」🔬<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://facebook.com/groups/banTVBteam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Fgroups%2FbanTVBteam&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDq6fvQnHzZYMiebojCBKDlo%3D&h=e141e0f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://facebook.com/groups/banTVBteam</a><br />\nTelegram: <a href=\"https://t.me/noTVBteam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FnoTVBteam&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDq6fvQnHzZYMiebojCBKDlo%3D&h=93d63042\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/noTVBteam</a><br />\n<br />\n請支持「抵制TVB運動」📡<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://facebook.com/banTVB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2FbanTVB&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDq6fvQnHzZYMiebojCBKDlo%3D&h=8b2b0a91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://facebook.com/banTVB</a> <br />\nTelegram: <a href=\"https://t.me/noTVB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FnoTVB&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDq6fvQnHzZYMiebojCBKDlo%3D&h=b1f908d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/noTVB</a>"},{"pid":"abfc42d0c41475d1a588076cf94beec0d97dfbfc","tid":1257415,"uid":217418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T15:08:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"35cdf1432313d626960908ca26396f315702ea50","tid":1257415,"uid":217418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T15:09:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0ad951e92e3bb64c28f06e9e56422ae5cabf5d75","tid":1257415,"uid":217418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"